text: Noa Diorgina Man (born 11 December 2004) is a Dutch freerunner. Man started with freerunning when she was 12 years old. When Man was 13 years old, she became senior national champion. In 2021 she won the Red Bull Art of Motion. At the Parkour competitions at the 2022 World Games she won the gold medal in the freestyle event and the silver medal in the speedrun event. ==References== Category:2004 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch sportspeople Category:Sportswomen
